quran[31]{c,v,t}:
  77,20,"Mbele min tagaani mon e ndiyam koy…óam."
  77,21,"Min mba…ói …óam e rannga ku…ďandiinga."
  77,22,"Ha e happu ganndaa…óo."
  77,23,"Min koddiri mbo mo∆ī∆īi …ďe hoddiroo…ďe."
  77,24,"Nden √Īalnde, bone woodanii yeddu…ďe …ďeen."
  77,25,"Mbele min mba…óaani leydi coomoori mon."
  77,26,"Wuur…ďe e maay…ďe(fof)."
  77,27,"Min mba…ói e hendi peŇč…óe toow…óe min njarni mon ndiyam mbel…óam."
  77,28,"Nden √Īalnde, bone woodanii yeddu…ďe …ďeen."
  77,29,"Pokkitane fa'ade ko njeddatna…óon."
  77,30,"Pokkitane fa'ade e …óowdi ndi …óem…óe tati."
  77,31,"Ndi …óowdinta nafata e lew lewndu."
  77,32,"Honge werno peete mawe hono ku…ďeeje."
  77,33,"Elle ko…óe geloo…ďi cooyi."
  77,34,"Nden √Īalnde, bone woodanii yeddu…ďe …ďeen."
  77,35,"E o √Īalngu …ďe kaalata."
  77,36,"∆Āe cakkitantaake saba …ďe ngantina."
  77,37,"Nden √Īalnde, bone woodanii yeddu…ďe …ďeen."
  77,38,"O ko √Īalawma ceerndu…óa min ndenndinii on wond'ude e adii…ďe …ďe."
  77,39,"Si tawii ho…óon njogi fehre pewjanee kam."
  77,40,"Nden √Īalnde, bone woodanii yeddu…ďe …ďeen."
  77,41,"Pellet, gooŇč…óu…ďe …ďeen ngonii e …óowdiiji e …ďulli."
  77,42,"E …ďesnooje ko…ďe tuuyate."
  77,43,"[∆Āe mbi'anee] : "√Īaamee njarone, ko newi mo…ódu, sabu kon ko ngollayno…óon."
  77,44,"Ko non woni ko min mbarjorta mo∆ī∆īim…ďe …ďeen."
  77,45,"Nden √Īalnde, bone woodanii yeddu…ďe …ďeen."
  77,46,"√Īaame ndakmita…óon see…óa ko on bannddiiji."
  77,47,"Nden √Īalnde, bone woodanii yeddu…ďe …ďeen."
  77,48,"Si…ďe mbiyaama nduk∆īe …ďe nduk∆īatah."
  77,49,"Nden √Īalnde, bone woodanii yeddu…ďe …ďeen."
  77,50,"Honde yeewtere caggal oon …ďe gooŇč…óinta."